                        "text": "FinancialPoolManager._generateRandom(uint256,uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#311-323) uses a weak PRNG: \"uint256(keccak256(bytes)(abi.encodePacked(block.timestamp,block.prevrandao,msg.sender,poolId,pools[poolId].winnersCount))) % max (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#312-322)\" \n"
