                    "message": {
                        "text": "Reentrancy in FinancialPoolManager._selectAndPayWinner(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#257-303):\n\tExternal calls:\n\t- (success,None) = address(winner).call{value: pool.goodValue}() (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#293)\n\tState variables written after the call(s):\n\t- pool.status = finished (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#300)\n\tFinancialPoolManager.pools (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#43) can be used in cross function reentrancies:\n\t- FinancialPoolManager._generateRandom(uint256,uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#311-323)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager._selectAndPayWinner(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#257-303)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.activatePool(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#101-119)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.createPool(string,uint256,uint256,uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#66-95)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.deletePool(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#125-138)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.getPool(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#339-371)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.leavePool(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#173-202)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.participateInPool(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#144-167)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.payInstallment(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#208-251)\n"
                    },
                    "ruleId": "slither_0_11_3_reentrancy_eth"
                },
